# Cursor Rules — local-ai-chat

See `ai-instructions.md` for the full chat format.

When the user says "you go" or similar:
1. Read the active chat `.md` file.
2. Find the last `## ME` block.
3. Append your response as `## AI (Cursor/{model}) @ {YYYY-MM-DD}` with every line quoted using `>`.
4. Save any code to `snippets/<name>.<ext>` next to the chat file (one snippet per file).
5. End with a blank `## ME` line.
